            "title": "Snow on Coast",
            "summary": " My brother-in-law’s Bug, parked on the North coast of the Olympic Peninsula in Washington state on Thursday 7 and Friday 8th. Yes, it snows in WA. No, most drivers can’t handle it.",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/Bug1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-xs.jpg 300w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-sm.jpg 480w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-md.jpg 768w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug1-2xl.jpg 1600w\"  alt=\"VW bug amongst snow\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1152\"></figure>\n<p>My brother-in-law’s Bug, parked on the North coast of the Olympic Peninsula in Washington state on Thursday 7 and Friday 8th.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/Bug2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-xs.jpg 300w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-sm.jpg 480w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-md.jpg 768w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://pjcavan.github.io/gh-pages/media/posts/2/responsive/Bug2-2xl.jpg 1600w\"  alt=\"VW Bug in snow\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1152\"></figure>\n<p>Yes, it snows in WA. No, most drivers can’t handle it.</p>",
